{"tid":2492090,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Dr. Peter Navarro: 最簡單的解釋也是最正確的解釋是 —— 武漢肺炎來自武漢實驗室","createTime":"2021-04-16T23:08:09.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-16T23:46:33.000Z","uid":226955,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"28f3d8a6a3df213fb1a3016dd93ab1f184589cb6","tid":2492090,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T23:08:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://amp.washingtontimes.com/news/2021/apr/13/is-dr-fauci-the-father-of-the-pandemic/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Famp.washingtontimes.com%2Fnews%2F2021%2Fapr%2F13%2Fis-dr-fauci-the-father-of-the-pandemic%2F&d=8tl7d8txXkgslZB5fT8CL3yU4AarvyINc8S1qmu5ZLM%3D&h=c35f7fc8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://amp.washingtontimes.com/news/2021/apr/13/is-dr-fauci-the-father-of-the-pandemic/</a><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>There is also the logic of Occam&rsquo;s razor: If a deadly virus pops up within several kilometers of the only bio-weapons lab in Asia, the simplest explanation, according to Occam&rsquo;s razor, is usually the right one. Ergo, SARS-CoV-2 came from the Wuhan Lab.</blockquote>"},{"pid":"afbc06c5a5241054f705bdd9f0fe52dc5133d8ff","tid":2492090,"uid":230703,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T23:08:55.000Z","msg":"點解佢會知？？"},{"pid":"f3fd3449a6ba17e0a743c16c5dbdf7bed5bdcdc5","tid":2492090,"uid":226955,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"afbc06c5a5241054f705bdd9f0fe52dc5133d8ff","tid":2492090,"uid":230703,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T23:08:55.000Z","msg":"點解佢會知？？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T23:11:50.000Z","msg":"推敲，但好合理<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>The wet market theory has recent historical precedent. China&rsquo;s first SARS virus, SARS-CoV-1, was quickly tracked to an almost identical virus found in raccoon dogs and Himalayan palm civet cats eaten in wet markets.<br />\n<br />\nYet after testing thousands of animals, no virologist has found a similar &ldquo;direct progenitor&rdquo; of China&rsquo;s second SARS virus. It is therefore extremely unlikely SARS-CoV-2 came from the Wuhan wet market. That leaves the competing Wuhan Lab theory.<br />\n<br />\nWith a biosafety rating of &ldquo;P4,&rdquo; the Wuhan Virology Lab houses the most dangerous pathogens on Earth, including the deadly Ebola. However, no P4 lab is ever 100% secure as there are numerous examples of pathogens escaping.<br />\n<br />\nAn accidental release of SARS-CoV-2 from the Wuhan Lab is therefore well within reason. This is particularly plausible given a U.S. State Department 2018 warning of sloppy safety precautions at the Wuhan Lab and the possibility of a &ldquo;new SARS-like pandemic.&rdquo; (You can&rsquo;t say we weren&rsquo;t warned.)</blockquote>"},{"pid":"db0c3fd33d8fbfa5f376134f0465e6b4d8b1bfd9","tid":2492090,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T23:13:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/miracle.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06aed9e8ccf971583d7a839aea902951a04e5b1d","tid":2492090,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T23:14:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/miracle.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"162260af39c5d0a20d944373962f51d1f7a36b8f","tid":2492090,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T23:15:49.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"510b8e6138bfec3c88ce8dfa8765e46e4a95bfad","tid":2492090,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T23:22:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/miracle.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0ec83f9c3afb727c6f7b213da2d7c0e154f985c","tid":2492090,"uid":294518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T23:45:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9479cb88a12d2613ae56bca944f2b396ab511654","tid":2492090,"uid":294518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T23:46:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/xi_GLB/status/1382652288544563204?s=20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fxi_GLB%2Fstatus%2F1382652288544563204%3Fs%3D20&d=8tl7d8txXkgslZB5fT8CL3yU4AarvyINc8S1qmu5ZLM%3D&h=f1f9f20e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fxi_GLB%2Fstatus%2F1382652288544563204%3Fs%3D20&h=7a338395\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/xi_GLB/status/1382652288544563204?s=20</a>"}]}